title: Winnie-the-Pooh Collection (twenty stories; cast incl. Stephen F
description:
Winnie-the-Pooh Collection

Starring:
Pooh - Stephen Fry
Piglet - Jane Horrocks
Eeyore - Geoffrey Palmer
Kanga - Judi Dench
Roo - Finty Williams
Rabbit - Robert Daws
Owl - Michael Williams
Christopher Robin - Steven Webb

Collection of stories appearing in Winnie-the-Pooh (1926) and The House at Pooh Corner (1928) read by a full cast. Twenty stories split across six CDs.
